        <title type="html"><![CDATA[可能出现的意外及解决方法（建议看完全部再开始）]]></title>
        <id>https://ulpaq8.coding-pages.com/post/xtcuproot-Q&amp;A/</id>
        <link href="https://ulpaq8.coding-pages.com/post/xtcuproot-Q&amp;A/">
        </link>
        <updated>2020-07-26T13:01:53.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- more -->
<p>开机后掉root了<br>
1、输入<code>adb reboot recovery</code>进入rec<br>
<img src="https://ulpaq8.coding-pages.com/post-images/1595768120423.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
2、点击   Install<br>
<img src="https://ulpaq8.coding-pages.com/post-images/1595768363476.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
接下来有两种方法<br>
方法1<br>
3-1-1、（需提前把<a href="https://xrzyun.coding.net/s/6ab049e5-ae03-4477-8ad4-3c16a523dc4e">magisk[下载]</a>导入/sdcard/）点击Install Zip<br>
<img src="https://ulpaq8.coding-pages.com/post-images/1595768843955.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
3-1-2、在列表中找到magisk的zip，点击滑动刷入，跑完之后，重启手表，成功</p>
<p>方法2<br>
3-2-1、（需连接手表）点击ADB Sideload<br>
<img src="https://ulpaq8.coding-pages.com/post-images/1595769105481.jpg" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
3-2-2、滑动开启此模式<br>
3-2-3、连接手表，打开<a href="https://lsdy.lanzous.com/b0bwa7gif">搞机助手[下载]</a><br>
3-2-4、连接成功，点击 恢复模式<br>
<img src="https://ulpaq8.coding-pages.com/post-images/1595769582615.PNG" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
3-2-5、点击Sideload 刷机模式<br>
<img src="https://ulpaq8.coding-pages.com/post-images/1595769705318.PNG" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
3-2-6、选择刷机包，<a href="https://xrzyun.coding.net/s/6ab049e5-ae03-4477-8ad4-3c16a523dc4e">magisk的zip[下载]</a>，开始刷机，跑完之后，重启手表，成功<br>
<img src="https://ulpaq8.coding-pages.com/post-images/1595770169698.PNG" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
